1. *Osećate* li još uvek umor? (Do you still feel tired?)
2. Oni su *osećali* kako im se srce rastvara. (They felt their hearts melting.)
3. Ona je *osećala* zebnju da se stvari počnu komplikovati. (She felt anxiety that things were going to get complicated.)
4. Oni su *osećali* da je nešto u vazduhu. (They felt that something was in the air.)
5. Nije bilo druge nego da *osećamo* bolnu istinu. (There was no other way but to feel the bitter truth.)